snippet.title: Forza Horizon 2 [PEGI 7] - E3 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Forza Horizon 2 is an action-packed, open-world driving game filled with beautiful vistas, amazing music and the world's greatest cars, including the video game premiere of the Lamborghini Huracán.
